# Self-hosted MediaPipe assets. The WASM runtime is copied from
# node_modules by scripts/setup-mediapipe.mjs at predev/prebuild time —
# regenerated on every build, so it stays ignored. The face-landmarker
# model is vendored (committed) so the build is hermetic and never depends
# on egress to storage.googleapis.com at build time — track it explicitly.
public/mediapipe/wasm/
!public/mediapipe/models/face_landmarker.task
